@node Introduct
Introduction
~~~~~~~~~~~~
ViewJPG shows JPEG images on PICASSO II boards. The program  uses  the
"Tower JPEG codec"  from Christoph Feck which is included in the "JFIF
Datatype" distribution. So it's neccessary to  install  this  datatype
before. The "JFIF Datatype" can be found on Aminet.
@endnode

